name: Monumen Batas Klungkung dan Gianyar
address: F947+JFH, Jalan Raya, Tusan, Kec. Banjarangkan, Kabupaten Klungkung, Bali 80515, Indonesia
review 1: Good view (check the photos I shared). This place just like a rest area when entering Klungkung Regency when come from Gianyar, Ubud, or Denpasar. The light in the night makes this place become more interesting to visit.
review 2: Each kabupaten (district) marks it boarders with some signpost. Over the years the size and opulence of the signposts increased. Also this one on the border between Klungkung and Gianyar district and built in 2018. It is really big and show most balinese/ hindoe motives. Well worth a stop and have a look. In the evening it becomes more beautiful with spectacular lights.
review 5: Nice monument for break and look around...
